---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "A Consumer Guide to Reviewing Daily Wellness Products Before You Buy";
const description = "Learn what to review before choosing a daily wellness product — ingredients, directions, safety information, and purchasing tips.";
const ctaTopo = "https://c2d6ddnxbtgz2r61fh0em90ofn.hop.clickbank.net/";
const ctaMeio = "https://c2d6ddnxbtgz2r61fh0em90ofn.hop.clickbank.net/";
const ctaFinal = "https://c2d6ddnxbtgz2r61fh0em90ofn.hop.clickbank.net/";
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#163226" />

    <!-- ============================================================
         ① META PIXEL (FACEBOOK)
         Substitua YOUR_PIXEL_ID pelo seu ID real do Meta Pixel
    ============================================================ -->
    <script is:inline>
      !function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s){
        if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?
        n.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};
        if(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version='2.0';
        n.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;
        t.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];
        s.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window,document,'script',
        'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js');
      fbq('init', 'YOUR_PIXEL_ID');
      fbq('track', 'PageView');
    </script>

    <!-- ============================================================
         ② GOOGLE TAG (GA4 + Google Ads)
    ============================================================ -->
    <script is:inline>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());
      gtag('config', 'G-YP7930G972');
      gtag('config', 'AW-18062534244');
    </script>

    <style>
      /* ===================== RESET & BASE ===================== */
      :global(*) {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      :global(html) {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      :global(body) {
        margin: 0;
        background: #f5f5f0;
        color: #2d3932;
        font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      :global(a) {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      :global(img) {
        display: block;
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      /* ===================== TOP BAR ===================== */
      .top-bar {
        padding: 8px 16px;
        background: #1a1a2e;
        color: #d5d5d5;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        line-height: 1.5;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .top-bar span {
        color: #e8c46a;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      /* ===================== HEADER ===================== */
      .site-header {
        border-bottom: 3px solid #2e7d32;
        background: #ffffff;
      }

      .header-inner {
        display: flex;
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 14px 20px;
        gap: 20px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .site-logo {
        color: #1a1a2e;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 19px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.6px;
      }

      .site-logo span {
        color: #2e7d32;
      }

      .header-nav {
        display: flex;
        color: #667069;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .header-nav a:hover,
      .header-nav a:focus-visible {
        color: #2e7d32;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
      }

      /* ===================== PAGE STRUCTURE ===================== */
      .page-wrapper {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 300px;
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        padding: 0 16px;
        gap: 30px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .main-content {
        padding: 36px 40px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 7%);
      }

      /* ===================== ARTICLE HEADER ===================== */
      .article-meta {
        display: flex;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        color: #7b847e;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 12px;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .article-meta .tag {
        padding: 3px 10px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: #e8f5e9;
        color: #26722d;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .article-title {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: #1a1a2e;
        font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 31px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      .article-subtitle {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        padding-left: 14px;
        border-left: 4px solid #2e7d32;
        color: #555f58;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-style: italic;
      }

      .intro-bullets {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .intro-bullets li {
        display: flex;
        padding: 6px 0;
        color: #333d36;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 15px;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .intro-bullets li::before {
        color: #2e7d32;
        content: '✓';
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.35;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      /* ===================== DISCLOSURES ===================== */
      .affiliate-disclosure {
        margin: 22px 0;
        padding: 15px 18px;
        border: 1px solid #ead39b;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #fff9e7;
        color: #624d17;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .affiliate-disclosure strong {
        color: #4d3b0e;
      }

      .medical-note {
        margin: 24px 0;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        border-left: 5px solid #2e7d32;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        background: #edf7ee;
        color: #31533a;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .medical-note strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        color: #1f5d2a;
      }

      /* ===================== CTA ===================== */
      .cta-btn {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 22px 0 10px;
        padding: 16px 24px;
        border: 0;
        border-radius: 50px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2e7d32, #43a047);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgb(46 125 50 / 36%);
        color: #ffffff !important;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
        line-height: 1.35;
        outline: none;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition:
          transform 0.2s ease,
          box-shadow 0.2s ease,
          background 0.2s ease;
      }

      .cta-btn:hover,
      .cta-btn:focus-visible {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #216b2a, #368b3d);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgb(46 125 50 / 44%);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .cta-btn small {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 4px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 400;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .cta-disclaimer {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        color: #818b84;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 11px;
        line-height: 1.55;
        text-align: center;
      }

      /* ===================== IMAGES ===================== */
      .hero-image-wrap {
        margin: 28px -40px;
      }

      .hero-image-wrap img {
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 400px;
        border-radius: 0;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .mid-image-wrap {
        margin: 28px 0;
      }

      .mid-image-wrap img {
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 380px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .image-caption {
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        color: #8b948e;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-style: italic;
        line-height: 1.5;
        text-align: center;
      }

      /* ===================== TEXT ===================== */
      p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: #3a453e;
      }

      h2.section-title {
        margin: 34px 0 14px;
        padding-bottom: 8px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #e8f5e9;
        color: #1a1a2e;
        font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }

      h3.sub-title {
        margin: 26px 0 10px;
        color: #2e7d32;
        font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .highlight-box {
        margin: 24px 0;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        border-left: 5px solid #f0a11f;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        background: #fffde7;
        color: #594816;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .highlight-box strong {
        color: #a75c00;
      }

      /* ===================== REVIEW CHECKLIST ===================== */
      .checklist-box {
        margin: 26px 0;
        padding: 22px;
        border: 1px solid #dce7dd;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #f9fcf9;
      }

      .checklist-box h3 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: #1c5728;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 15px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .checklist-box ul {
        display: grid;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        gap: 9px;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .checklist-box li {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 25px;
        color: #46544b;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .checklist-box li::before {
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #2e7d32;
        content: '✓';
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      /* ===================== INGREDIENT CARDS ===================== */
      .ingredient-card {
        display: flex;
        margin: 14px 0;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e0e4e0;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #fafafa;
        gap: 14px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .ingredient-card .ing-icon {
        font-size: 30px;
        line-height: 1.2;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .ingredient-card h4 {
        margin: 0 0 4px;
        color: #1a1a2e;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .ingredient-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #59645e;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      /* ===================== ROUTINE ===================== */
      .routine-steps {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 0;
        counter-reset: step;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .routine-steps li {
        display: flex;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #f8faf8;
        counter-increment: step;
        gap: 16px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .routine-steps li::before {
        display: flex;
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #2e7d32;
        color: #ffffff;
        content: counter(step);
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 800;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .routine-steps li p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #465249;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .routine-steps li strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 2px;
        color: #1a1a2e;
      }

      /* ===================== ARTICLE FOOTER ===================== */
      .article-footer {
        margin-top: 38px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        color: #7d8780;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .article-footer p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #68736b;
      }

      .article-footer strong {
        color: #404d44;
      }

      /* ===================== SIDEBAR ===================== */
      .sidebar {
        display: flex;
        position: sticky;
        top: 20px;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .sidebar-box {
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 8%);
      }

      .sidebar-box h3 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #e8f5e9;
        color: #1a1a2e;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .sidebar-box p {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: #59645e;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .sidebar-image {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto 14px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .sidebar-product-image {
        width: 160px;
        margin: 0 auto 14px;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .sidebar-cta {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 8px;
        padding: 13px 16px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2e7d32, #43a047);
        box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgb(46 125 50 / 32%);
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.35;
        text-align: center;
        transition:
          transform 0.2s ease,
          box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }

      .sidebar-cta:hover,
      .sidebar-cta:focus-visible {
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgb(46 125 50 / 40%);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .summary-list {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .summary-list li {
        display: flex;
        padding: 7px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #edf0ed;
        color: #465249;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        gap: 8px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .summary-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: 0;
      }

      .summary-list li::before {
        color: #2e7d32;
        content: '•';
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      .reminder-box {
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border: 1px solid #ffe082;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #fff8e1;
      }

      .reminder-box h4 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        color: #a95e00;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .reminder-box p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #715a15;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      /* ===================== FOOTER ===================== */
      .site-footer {
        margin-top: 50px;
        padding: 25px 20px;
        background: #1a1a2e;
        color: #afb5b0;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 11px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .site-footer p {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 7px;
        color: #afb5b0;
      }

      .site-footer a {
        color: #9fd5a3;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 2px;
      }

      /* ===================== RESPONSIVE ===================== */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .page-wrapper {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .sidebar {
          position: static;
        }

        .main-content {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }

        .hero-image-wrap {
          margin: 24px -20px;
        }

        .article-title {
          font-size: 25px;
        }

        .header-nav {
          display: none;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .header-inner {
          padding: 13px 16px;
        }

        .page-wrapper {
          margin: 22px auto;
          padding: 0 12px;
        }

        .main-content {
          padding: 22px 16px;
        }

        .hero-image-wrap {
          margin: 22px -16px;
        }

        .cta-btn {
          padding: 15px 18px;
          font-size: 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- ===== TOP BAR ===== -->
  <div class="top-bar">
    <span>WELLNESS EDUCATION</span>
    — Independent Consumer Information Resource
  </div>

  <!-- ===== SITE HEADER ===== -->
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="header-inner">
      <a class="site-logo" href="/">
        Natural<span>Tonic</span>Routine
      </a>

      <nav class="header-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="#product-review">Product Review</a>
        <a href="#ingredients">Ingredients</a>
        <a href="#routine">Daily Routine</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ===== PAGE WRAPPER ===== -->
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <main class="main-content">
      <div class="article-meta">
        <span class="tag">Wellness Education</span>
        <span>Updated: July 2026</span>
        <span>Reading Time: 6 minutes</span>
        <span>Independent Information</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="article-title">
        A Consumer Guide to Reviewing Daily Wellness Products Before You Buy
      </h1>

      <p class="article-subtitle">
        Before choosing a wellness product, it is helpful to review the ingredients,
        preparation instructions, safety information, and current details available
        on the official product website.
      </p>

      <ul class="intro-bullets">
        <li>Learn which product details are important to review.</li>
        <li>Understand how to check ingredient and serving information.</li>
        <li>Explore practical questions to consider before purchasing.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="affiliate-disclosure" role="note">
        <strong>Affiliate Disclosure:</strong>
        This page contains affiliate links. If you purchase through one of these
        links, Natural Tonic Routine may receive a commission at no additional cost
        to you. Please review the official product information before making a
        purchase decision.
      </div>

      <a
        href={ctaTopo}
        class="cta-btn"
        target="_blank"
        rel="nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Visit the Official Product Website
        <small>Review current ingredients, directions, pricing, and policies</small>
      </a>

      <p class="cta-disclaimer">
        This content is for educational purposes only and is not medical advice.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-image-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/presell/v1-advertorial/jogging-couple.webp"
          alt="Two adults jogging outdoors together"
          loading="eager"
          width="900"
          height="450"
        />
        <p class="image-caption">
          Daily movement and other consistent lifestyle habits can be meaningful
          parts of an overall wellness routine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Many people look for practical ways to create routines that feel manageable
        over time. A daily wellness product may be one option some consumers choose
        to explore, alongside nutrition, hydration, movement, rest, and appropriate
        healthcare guidance.
      </p>

      <p>
        Before adding any supplement to a routine, it is important to understand
        what the product contains, how it is intended to be used, and whether it is
        suitable for your individual circumstances.
      </p>

      <div class="medical-note" role="note">
        <strong>Important health reminder</strong>
        No supplement replaces a balanced diet, regular movement, sufficient rest,
        or advice from a qualified healthcare professional. Consult a healthcare
        professional before using a new dietary supplement, especially if you are
        pregnant, nursing, have a medical condition, or use medication.
      </div>

      <section id="product-review">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          What to Review Before Choosing a Wellness Product
        </h2>

        <p>
          Marketing messages can be brief, but product decisions deserve more
          careful consideration. A useful starting point is to focus on the label,
          instructions, policies, and any safety information provided by the
          manufacturer.
        </p>

        <div class="checklist-box">
          <h3>Consumer Review Checklist</h3>

          <ul>
            <li>Read the complete ingredient list and serving size.</li>
            <li>Check for allergens, dietary restrictions, or personal sensitivities.</li>
            <li>Review the manufacturer's suggested use and storage directions.</li>
            <li>Check the official website for current pricing and purchase policies.</li>
            <li>Review refund, shipping, and subscription information before ordering.</li>
            <li>Consult a healthcare professional when appropriate.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>
          The official product website is generally the best source for the latest
          details about formula changes, recommended use, package options, and
          purchasing terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="mid-image-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/presell/v1-advertorial/man-walking-nature-trail.webp"
          alt="Adult walking on a nature trail"
          loading="lazy"
          width="760"
          height="380"
        />
        <p class="image-caption">
          Walking, hydration, balanced meals, and other realistic habits can be
          considered as part of a personal routine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Why Simple and Consistent Habits Matter
        </h2>

        <p>
          Many people prefer routines that are straightforward and compatible with
          their daily schedule. A routine does not need to be complicated to be
          meaningful; consistency and personal suitability are often more important
          than trying to follow an overly restrictive plan.
        </p>

        <p>
          When considering a product, focus on whether its directions are clear,
          whether the ingredient information is available, and whether it can be
          evaluated responsibly in the context of your own lifestyle and health
          needs.
        </p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          <strong>Consumer tip:</strong>
          Avoid relying on a single product as the foundation of your wellness
          routine. Consider it only as one possible addition to broader lifestyle
          habits and professional guidance when needed.
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="ingredients">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Understanding Ingredient Information
